You have found the missing dwarf-adventurer
The dwarf-merchant, bringer of supplies, went missing at the very beginning of the expedition, even before you arrived to assist the dwarves.
The dwarf-miner was a stout worker for Brogur and BÃ³si's cause, and greatly desired to lay eyes upon the lost Mines of Moria during the course of his life.

You have found the missing dwarf-warrior
The dwarf-adventurer feared nothing as he set his sights on Moria, but the Watcher put an end to his eagerness.
The fearless dwarf-warrior looks as though he would not go down without a fight, and from the look of it he put some fear into the enemy ere he fell.
